00:26:36.553 --> 00:26:37.762
<font color="white">when you killed my brother.</font><font color="white"></font>

332
00:26:40.015 --> 00:26:40.849
<font color="white">Your brother?</font><font color="white"></font>

333
00:26:58.950 --> 00:26:59.993
<font color="white">How much longer?</font><font color="white"></font>

334
00:27:01.703 --> 00:27:03.204
<font color="white">We're 20 minutes away. sir.</font><font color="white"></font>

335
00:27:04.998 --> 00:27:07.500
