<font color="white">-Yes. sir.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

336
00:27:08.418 --> 00:27:11.087
<font color="white">All units proceed to the destination.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">except for the lead vehicle.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

337
00:27:11.171 --> 00:27:12.630
<font color="white">We'll secure the area and stand by.</font><font color="white"></font>

338
00:27:32.484 --> 00:27:34.277
<font color="white">Seriously. man!</font><font color="white"></font>

339
00:27:35.528 --> 00:27:37.906
<font color="white">I think my ears are bleeding!</font><font color="white"></font>

340
00:27:39.491 --> 00:27:41.493
<font color="white">-I can taste blood!</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Turn it off!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

341
00:27:41.576 --> 00:27:42.619
<font color="white">Just enjoy it!</font><font color="white"></font>

342
00:27:46.289 --> 00:27:47.499
<font color="white">Hey!</font><font color="white"></font>

343
00:27:47.582 --> 00:27:49.459
<font color="white">Try to hold out… Are you listening?</font><font color="white"></font>

344
00:27:49.542 --> 00:27:52.295
<font color="white">Hey. you guys try to hold out</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">until I get back!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

345
00:27:52.379 --> 00:27:54.923
<font color="white">-Don't get scared and cry! Got it?</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Just go already.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

346
00:27:55.006 --> 00:27:57.550
<font color="white">Rock spirit!</font><font color="white"></font>

347
00:27:59.886 --> 00:28:01.221
<font color="white">What's that lunatic even saying?</font><font color="white"></font>

348
00:28:40.135 --> 00:28:41.010
<font color="white">Your brother?</font><font color="white"></font>

349
00:28:42.595 --> 00:28:43.888
<font color="white">What do you mean?</font><font color="white"></font>

350
00:28:44.639 --> 00:28:45.890
<font color="white">You killed him.</font><font color="white"></font>

351
00:28:50.145 --> 00:28:52.188
<font color="white">I'm talking about Number 66.</font><font color="white"></font>

352
00:28:57.861 --> 00:28:58.862
<font color="white">Are you…</font><font color="white"></font>

353
00:29:10.498 --> 00:29:11.332
<font color="white">Are you…</font><font color="white"></font>

354
00:29:13.209 --> 00:29:14.377
<font color="white">Gang Seong?</font><font color="white"></font>

355
00:29:16.171 --> 00:29:18.256
<font color="white">Yeong Gwang!</font><font color="white"></font>

356
00:29:19.215 --> 00:29:20.675
<font color="white">-Gang Seong!</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Yeong Gwang!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

357
00:29:20.759 --> 00:29:24.721
<font color="white">-Go back! Right now!</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Yeong Gwang!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

358
00:29:25.305 --> 00:29:26.973
<font color="white">Don't leave me behind!</font><font color="white"></font>

359
00:29:27.056 --> 00:29:27.891
<font color="white">-Yeong Gwang!</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Wait for me!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

360
00:29:27.974 --> 00:29:30.185
<font color="white">I promise to succeed</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">and come back for you!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

361
00:29:30.810 --> 00:29:33.146
<font color="white">-Stay alive! You have to survive. okay?</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Yeong Gwang!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

362
00:29:33.229 --> 00:29:35.315
<font color="white">-Yeong Gwang!</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">-Wait for me. Gang Seong!</font><font color="white"></font></font>

363
00:29:49.662 --> 00:29:50.538
<font color="white">I'm not the one…</font><font color="white"></font>

364
00:29:52.415 --> 00:29:53.708
<font color="white">who killed your brother.</font><font color="white"></font>

365
00:30:05.386 --> 00:30:08.223
<font color="white">CRUSH THE PROVOCATIVE SCHEMES</font><font color="white">
