366
00:30:54.018 --> 00:30:54.853
<font color="white">Enough.</font><font color="white"></font>

367
00:31:30.263 --> 00:31:31.097
<font color="white">Take it.</font><font color="white"></font>

368
00:31:33.224 --> 00:31:34.767
<font color="white">I'm giving it to you out of pity.</font><font color="white"></font>

369
00:31:35.351 --> 00:31:36.436
<font color="white">You keep losing to me.</font><font color="white"></font>

370
