<font color="white">so I was wondering</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">if it's because you don't eat enough.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

371
00:31:43.610 --> 00:31:44.444
<font color="white">Thanks.</font><font color="white"></font>

372
00:31:45.278 --> 00:31:46.154
<font color="white">I appreciate it.</font><font color="white"></font>

373
00:31:47.572 --> 00:31:48.489
<font color="white">You bastard.</font><font color="white"></font>

374
00:31:49.282 --> 00:31:50.408
<font color="white">Don't you have any pride?</font><font color="white"></font>

375
00:31:52.660 --> 00:31:54.871
<font color="white">There's no such thing as pride</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">between friends.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

376
00:31:58.791 --> 00:31:59.876
<font color="white">BETTER DEATH THAN ENEMY CAPTURE</font><font color="white"></font>

377
00:31:59.959 --> 00:32:01.085
<font color="white">Tomorrow's finally the day.</font><font color="white"></font>

378
00:32:01.961 --> 00:32:03.922
<font color="white">I'm going to make it back alive.</font><font color="white"></font>

379
00:32:05.882 --> 00:32:08.718
<font color="white">They said if we complete this operation.</font><font color="white"></font>

380
00:32:09.510 --> 00:32:11.596
<font color="white">they'll give us a house</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">and find our family.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

381
00:32:11.679 --> 00:32:12.931
<font color="white">Family. my foot.</font><font color="white"></font>

382
00:32:13.765 --> 00:32:16.059
<font color="white">I can't even remember my own name.</font><font color="white"></font>

383
00:32:18.269 --> 00:32:19.312
<font color="white">Kim.</font><font color="white"></font>

384
00:32:20.021 --> 00:32:21.147
<font color="white">Your last name is Kim.</font><font color="white"></font>

385
00:32:22.607 --> 00:32:23.483
<font color="white">What did you say?</font><font color="white"></font>

386
00:32:24.067 --> 00:32:25.777
<font color="white">Do you remember when we first came here?</font><font color="white"></font>

387
00:32:28.529 --> 00:32:30.239
