388
00:32:31.616 --> 00:32:33.326
<font color="white">I forgot my own name.</font><font color="white"></font>

389
00:32:34.744 --> 00:32:36.037
<font color="white">But for some reason.</font><font color="white"></font>

390
00:32:36.871 --> 00:32:39.749
<font color="white">I never forgot that your last name is Kim.</font><font color="white"></font>

391
00:32:42.251 --> 00:32:43.378
<font color="white">Isn't that funny?</font><font color="white"></font>

392
00:32:44.921 --> 00:32:47.340
<font color="white">I was so scared that I forgot my own name.</font><font color="white"></font>

393
00:32:47.423 --> 00:32:50.426
<font color="white">but I still remember your last name.</font><font color="white"></font>

394
00:32:55.640 --> 00:32:56.683
<font color="white">Kim…</font><font color="white"></font>

395
00:33:11.656 --> 00:33:13.199
<font color="white">Don't forget me.</font><font color="white"></font>

396
00:33:15.868 --> 00:33:17.704
<font color="white">You're my only friend.</font><font color="white"></font>

397
00:33:20.206 --> 00:33:21.582
<font color="white">If you forget me too…</font><font color="white"></font>

398
00:33:23.501 --> 00:33:25.837
<font color="white">there'll be no one left to remember me.</font><font color="white"></font>

399
00:33:31.759 --> 00:33:33.553
<font color="white">How can I forget my nemesis?</font><font color="white"></font>

400
00:33:35.346 --> 00:33:38.474
<font color="white">I'm 73. the Republic's pride and joy.</font><font color="white"></font>

401
00:33:39.308 --> 00:33:40.143
<font color="white">And you…</font><font color="white"></font>

402
00:33:41.144 --> 00:33:42.979
<font color="white">You're 66. a pile of dog crap.</font><font color="white"></font>

403
00:34:07.003 --> 00:34:08.171
<font color="white">Hey. 66!</font><font color="white"></font>

404
00:34:08.880 --> 00:34:09.964
<font color="white">Let's get out of here!</font><font color="white"></font>

405
00:34:19.515 --> 00:34:20.516
<font color="white">Hey. 66.</font><font color="white"></font>

406
00:34:28.608 --> 00:34:30.068
<font color="white">Get it together.</font><font color="white"></font>

407
00:34:30.860 --> 00:34:31.694
<font color="white">Let's get out of here.</font><font color="white"></font>

408
00:34:32.445 --> 00:34:33.279
<font color="white">Forget it.</font><font color="white"></font>

409
00:34:34.739 --> 00:34:35.990
<font color="white">Unless you can attach…</font><font color="white"></font>

410
00:34:38.034 --> 00:34:38.910
<font color="white">my leg.</font><font color="white"></font>

411
00:34:48.002 --> 00:34:48.920
<font color="white">Let's get out.</font><font color="white"></font>

412
00:34:50.296 --> 00:34:51.172
<font color="white">This is it…</font><font color="white"></font>

413
00:34:52.673 --> 00:34:54.175
<font color="white">for me.</font><font color="white"></font>

414
00:34:56.135 --> 00:34:57.720
<font color="white">You have to live.</font><font color="white"></font>

415
00:35:25.957 --> 00:35:27.959
<font color="white">I'd rather pull the trigger than survive…</font><font color="white"></font>

416
00:35:29.919 --> 00:35:30.878
<font color="white">and be taken as a prisoner.</font><font color="white"></font>

417
00:35:32.797 --> 00:35:34.382
<font color="white">I won't let you die alone.</font><font color="white"></font>

418
00:35:35.383 --> 00:35:36.384
<font color="white">We'll die together.</font><font color="white"></font>

419
00:35:58.573 --> 00:35:59.740
<font color="white">Don't die.</font><font color="white"></font>

420
00:36:01.033 --> 00:36:02.660
<font color="white">Think about why…</font><font color="white"></font>

421
00:36:04.370 --> 00:36:05.913
<font color="white">we endured that hell.</font><font color="white"></font>

422
00:36:10.001 --> 00:36:12.003
<font color="white">It was to survive.</font><font color="white"></font>

423
00:36:15.423 --> 00:36:17.800
<font color="white">I need you to do one last thing for me.</font><font color="white"></font>

424
00:36:25.933 --> 00:36:27.435
<font color="white">No matter what happens…</font><font color="white"></font>

425
00:36:29.520 --> 00:36:30.354
<font color="white">promise me…</font><font color="white"></font>

426
00:36:38.529 --> 00:36:39.989
<font color="white">you'll survive.</font><font color="white"></font>

427
00:37:14.440 --> 00:37:16.400
<font color="white">Drop your gun! Hands on your head.</font><font color="white"></font>

428
00:38:06.117 --> 00:38:07.201
<font color="white">Dad!</font><font color="white"></font>

429
00:38:09.370 --> 00:38:10.997
<font color="white">Don't you have any pride at all?</font><font color="white"></font>

430
00:38:12.373 --> 00:38:14.792
<font color="white">Why did you have to grovel and kneel?</font><font color="white"></font>

431
00:38:14.875 --> 00:38:17.003
<font color="white">Is it because Hye-ri's dad</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">is a powerful man?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

432
00:38:17.086 --> 00:38:18.629
<font color="white">I'm so ashamed.</font><font color="white"></font>

433
00:38:18.713 --> 00:38:21.674
<font color="white">I feel so angry. frustrated. and pathetic.</font><font color="white"></font>

434
00:38:22.717 --> 00:38:24.510
<font color="white">Why did you even have me?</font><font color="white"></font>

435
00:38:25.344 --> 00:38:26.178
<font color="white">Min-ji.</font><font color="white"></font>

436
00:38:36.564 --> 00:38:37.648
<font color="white">DAD</font><font color="white"></font>

437
00:38:37.732 --> 00:38:39.400
<font color="white"><i>I'm sorry for making you feel ashamed.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

438
00:38:40.276 --> 00:38:41.944
<font color="white"><i>But a parent's pride doesn't matter</i></font><font color="white"></font>

439
00:38:42.695 --> 00:38:44.613
<font color="white"><i>when it comes to their child.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

440
00:38:45.614 --> 00:38:46.449
<font color="white"><i>Min-ji.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

441
00:38:47.325 --> 00:38:48.159
<font color="white"><i>you're my pride.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

442
00:38:52.163 --> 00:38:53.581
<font color="white">I won't die. Dad.</font><font color="white"></font>

443
00:38:54.707 --> 00:38:56.917
<font color="white">I'm going to survive and make it home.</font><font color="white"></font>

444
00:39:30.743 --> 00:39:31.577
<font color="white">What now?</font><font color="white"></font>

445
00:39:34.330 --> 00:39:37.291
<font color="white">Seriously? Now it's pouring rain too?</font><font color="white"></font>

446
00:39:38.501 --> 00:39:40.252
<font color="white">You've got to be kidding me.</font><font color="white"></font>

447
00:39:40.336 --> 00:39:42.922
<font color="white">It's just one thing after another. huh?</font><font color="white"></font>

448
00:39:47.301 --> 00:39:48.219
<font color="white">Jeez.</font><font color="white"></font>

449
00:39:54.183 --> 00:39:55.643
<font color="white">Boss!</font><font color="white"></font>

450
00:39:57.395 --> 00:39:58.229
<font color="white">Gang-min!</font><font color="white"></font>

451
00:39:59.939 --> 00:40:01.857
<font color="white">Hey. Gang-min.</font><font color="white"></font>

452
00:40:01.941 --> 00:40:03.442
<font color="white">What's wrong with you? What happened?</font><font color="white"></font>

453
00:40:04.402 --> 00:40:05.861
<font color="white">A guy</font><font color="white"></font>

454
00:40:07.154 --> 00:40:10.282
<font color="white">claiming to be that girl's dad came and…</font><font color="white"></font>

455
00:40:12.326 --> 00:40:14.245
<font color="white">What? Her dad?</font><font color="white"></font>

456
00:40:14.328 --> 00:40:17.957
<font color="white">What are you talking about?</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">Why would her dad show up here?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

457
00:40:19.708 --> 00:40:20.918
<font color="white">Hey. Gang-min.</font><font color="white"></font>

458
00:40:23.045 --> 00:40:24.004
<font color="white">Is he dead?</font><font color="white"></font>

459
00:40:24.964 --> 00:40:26.507
<font color="white">Hey. Gang-min!</font><font color="white"></font>

460
00:40:35.266 --> 00:40:36.267
<font color="white">That's more like it.</font><font color="white"></font>

461
00:40:36.976 --> 00:40:39.770
<font color="white">This is how it should be.</font><font color="white"></font>

462
00:40:40.271 --> 00:40:42.106
<font color="white">You held out pretty long.</font><font color="white"></font>

463
00:40:43.107 --> 00:40:44.024
<font color="white">didn't you?</font><font color="white"></font>

464
00:41:06.005 --> 00:41:07.131
<font color="white">Hey. kid.</font><font color="white"></font>

465
00:41:10.676 --> 00:41:12.636
<font color="white">Why are you hiding?</font><font color="white"></font>

466
00:41:15.681 --> 00:41:18.058
<font color="white">Come on out. It's time to go home.</font><font color="white"></font>

467
00:41:21.729 --> 00:41:23.147
<font color="white">Oh. I see.</font><font color="white"></font>

468
00:41:24.690 --> 00:41:26.609
<font color="white">Are you letting me know where you are?</font><font color="white"></font>

469
00:41:29.195 --> 00:41:34.158
<font color="white">Should I fall for your little plan or not?</font><font color="white"></font>

470
00:41:35.701 --> 00:41:36.619
<font color="white">Let's say</font><font color="white"></font>

471
00:41:37.453 --> 00:41:39.955
<font color="white">I head over there…</font><font color="white"></font>

472
00:41:40.998 --> 00:41:42.291
<font color="white">Then you'll try to run!</font><font color="white"></font>

473
00:41:45.085 --> 00:41:47.171
<font color="white">Or you'll come up from behind!</font><font color="white"></font>

474
00:41:51.592 --> 00:41:52.426
<font color="white">Hey.</font><font color="white"></font>

475
00:41:53.177 --> 00:41:56.472
<font color="white">Stop playing games and come out.</font><font color="white"></font>

476
00:41:59.683 --> 00:42:01.602
<font color="white">Does it look like I'm messing around?</font><font color="white"></font>

477
00:42:02.561 --> 00:42:05.648
<font color="white">If you come out now. I'll let you go.</font><font color="white"></font>

478
00:42:05.731 --> 00:42:08.025
<font color="white">I'm done going easy on you!</font><font color="white"></font>

479
00:42:16.867 --> 00:42:17.952
<font color="white">Bullshit.</font><font color="white"></font>

480
00:42:30.422 --> 00:42:31.423
<font color="white">Hey. you're alive.</font><font color="white"></font>

481
00:42:32.007 --> 00:42:33.509
<font color="white">Where are you going? Come here.</font><font color="white"></font>

482
00:42:33.592 --> 00:42:34.802
<font color="white">Come here!</font><font color="white"></font>

483
00:43:27.479 --> 00:43:29.356
<font color="white">You almost had me fooled.</font><font color="white"></font>

484
00:43:31.942 --> 00:43:33.360
<font color="white">Don't bullshit me!</font><font color="white"></font>

485
00:43:36.113 --> 00:43:37.281
<font color="white">Whatever you say.</font><font color="white"></font>

486
00:43:38.657 --> 00:43:40.868
<font color="white">you're still nothing</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">but a traitor to the regime.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

487
00:43:42.077 --> 00:43:44.163
<font color="white">You think I'll believe anything you say?</font><font color="white"></font>

488
00:43:53.464 --> 00:43:54.798
<font color="white">You can believe me or not.</font><font color="white"></font>

489
00:43:56.508 --> 00:43:58.093
<font color="white">That's your choice.</font><font color="white"></font>

490
00:43:59.011 --> 00:44:00.095
<font color="white">But all of us…</font><font color="white"></font>

491
00:44:01.180 --> 00:44:02.306
<font color="white">were discarded.</font><font color="white"></font>

492
00:44:03.265 --> 00:44:04.391
<font color="white"><i>Have you thought about it?</i></font><font color="white"></font>

493
00:44:05.017 --> 00:44:06.727
<font color="white">I still don't understand.</font><font color="white"></font>

494
00:44:06.810 --> 00:44:09.313
<font color="white">Why do you people need me?</font><font color="white"></font>

495
00:44:09.396 --> 00:44:11.231
<font color="white">To be honest.</font><font color="white"></font>

496
00:44:11.315 --> 00:44:14.860
<font color="white">I think it's a waste</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">to throw away talent like yours.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

497
00:44:14.943 --> 00:44:19.114
<font color="white">I haven't seen anyone else</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">who can go toe-to-toe with Park Jin-cheol.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

498
00:44:19.740 --> 00:44:23.577
<font color="white">In fact. you're probably the only one</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">from the North who can.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

499
00:44:23.661 --> 00:44:25.329
<font color="white">This is your last chance.</font><font color="white"></font>

500
00:44:25.412 --> 00:44:28.999
<font color="white">If you continue to hold out.</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">we'll have no choice but to end you.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

501
00:44:30.292 --> 00:44:32.211
<font color="white">The North may have discarded you.</font><font color="white"></font>

502
00:44:32.294 --> 00:44:34.421
<font color="white">but you still need to find a way</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">to make a life here.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

503
00:44:34.505 --> 00:44:35.339
