01:02:35.209 --> 01:02:37.670
<font color="white">The only way this ends is by finding her.</font><font color="white"></font>

679
01:02:38.838 --> 01:02:40.965
<font color="white">So call me once you've tracked her.</font><font color="white"></font>

680
01:02:43.050 --> 01:02:44.719
<font color="white"><i>Please. Sang-a.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

681
01:02:59.108 --> 01:03:00.985
<font color="white">What kind of bullshit is that?</font><font color="white"></font>

682
01:03:01.068 --> 01:03:02.612
<font color="white">How can we trust that bastard?</font><font color="white"></font>

683
01:03:03.112 --> 01:03:05.531
<font color="white">Agent Kim is going out of control</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">to find his daughter.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

684
01:03:05.615 --> 01:03:07.283
<font color="white">Once he does.</font><font color="white"></font>

685
01:03:07.366 --> 01:03:09.452
<font color="white">he'll turn himself in.</font><font color="white"></font>

686
01:03:09.535 --> 01:03:10.745
<font color="white">What. you think he's crazy?</font><font color="white"></font>

687
01:03:11.412 --> 01:03:13.664
<font color="white">He knows exactly what will happen</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">if he turns himself in.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

688
01:03:13.748 --> 01:03:17.001
<font color="white">He's a man of his word.</font><font color="white"></font>

689
01:03:17.084 --> 01:03:17.960
<font color="white">Shut up. you punk!</font><font color="white"></font>

690
01:03:18.044 --> 01:03:19.128
<font color="white">I'm sorry. sir.</font><font color="white"></font>

691
01:03:20.254 --> 01:03:21.506
<font color="white">Sir.</font><font color="white"></font>

692
01:03:21.589 --> 01:03:23.257
<font color="white">I think they have a point.</font><font color="white"></font>

693
01:03:23.341 --> 01:03:24.258
<font color="white">I agree. sir.</font><font color="white"></font>

694
01:03:24.342 --> 01:03:27.011
<font color="white">Agent Kim's movements</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">have been centered around his daughter.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

695
01:03:27.595 --> 01:03:29.138
<font color="white">What's the matter with all of you?</font><font color="white"></font>

696
01:03:29.222 --> 01:03:31.557
<font color="white">Any dad would naturally…</font><font color="white"></font>

697
01:03:32.433 --> 01:03:34.018
<font color="white">It's only natural. isn't it?</font><font color="white"></font>

698
01:03:36.229 --> 01:03:38.940
<font color="white">So. his daughter is his weakness.</font><font color="white"></font>

699
01:03:41.275 --> 01:03:43.444
<font color="white">Look for Kim's daughter right now.</font><font color="white"></font>

700
01:03:44.070 --> 01:03:45.822
<font color="white">We need to take her hostage first.</font><font color="white"></font>

701
01:03:45.905 --> 01:03:46.781
<font color="white">Sorry?</font><font color="white"></font>

702
01:03:47.448 --> 01:03:48.282
<font color="white">Yes. sir.</font><font color="white"></font>

703
01:03:49.242 --> 01:03:50.493
<font color="white">Take her hostage?</font><font color="white"></font>

704
01:03:54.247 --> 01:03:57.583
<font color="white">Codename 66</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">entered Myeongpo Port at 23:01.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

705
01:03:58.084 --> 01:04:03.422
{\an8}<font color="white">CODENAME 66</font><font color="white"></font>

706
01:04:04.507 --> 01:04:08.177
{\an8}<font color="white">Subject who appears to be Kim Min-ji</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">sighted at 23:34.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

707
01:04:15.351 --> 01:04:18.312
<font color="white">Subject entered the road in question</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">at 23:45.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

708
01:04:22.149 --> 01:04:23.317
<font color="white">It's that car. right?</font><font color="white"></font>

709
01:04:23.943 --> 01:04:25.111
<font color="white">You sure she got in?</font><font color="white"></font>

710
01:04:25.194 --> 01:04:26.445
<font color="white">Yes. she did.</font><font color="white"></font>

711
01:04:26.529 --> 01:04:27.947
<font color="white">I'll track her location right now.</font><font color="white"></font>

712
01:04:28.030 --> 01:04:30.700
<font color="white">155D 9884</font><font color="white"></font>

713
01:04:35.955 --> 01:04:37.498
<font color="white">Thank you for giving me a ride.</font><font color="white"></font>

714
01:04:38.124 --> 01:04:39.166
<font color="white">Thank you so much.</font><font color="white"></font>

715
01:04:53.598 --> 01:04:54.599
<font color="white">You haven't found her yet?</font><font color="white"></font>

716
01:04:54.682 --> 01:04:55.808
<font color="white">We can't find her anywhere.</font><font color="white"></font>

717
01:04:57.101 --> 01:04:59.228
<font color="white">The lead vehicle just passed by here.</font><font color="white"></font>

718
01:05:00.521 --> 01:05:01.480
<font color="white">You mean the chairman?</font><font color="white"></font>

719
01:05:02.773 --> 01:05:04.233
<font color="white"><i>We're en route to the villa.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

720
01:05:04.901 --> 01:05:05.818
<font color="white">Understood.</font><font color="white"></font>

721
01:05:07.194 --> 01:05:08.988
<font color="white">Mr. Nam will join us shortly.</font><font color="white"></font>

722
01:05:13.159 --> 01:05:14.201
<font color="white">The rain stopped.</font><font color="white"></font>

723
01:05:17.663 --> 01:05:18.497
<font color="white">Jung.</font><font color="white"></font>

724
01:05:19.874 --> 01:05:22.168
<font color="white">-Do you know what </font><font color="white"><font color="white"><i>hojae</i></font></font><font color="white"><font color="white"> means?</font><font color="white"></font>
<font color="white">-Excuse me?</font><font color="white"></font></font>

725
01:05:23.127 --> 01:05:24.754
<font color="white">Doesn't it mean a good thing?</font><font color="white"></font>

726
01:05:25.463 --> 01:05:26.297
<font color="white">That's right.</font><font color="white"></font>

727
01:05:27.423 --> 01:05:29.508
<font color="white">Any factor that provides a good advantage.</font><font color="white"></font>

728
01:05:32.678 --> 01:05:34.513
<font color="white">It can also mean "good material."</font><font color="white"></font>

729
01:05:36.140 --> 01:05:36.974
<font color="white">I'll remember that. sir.</font><font color="white"></font>

730
01:05:39.518 --> 01:05:40.853
<font color="white">An unexpected advantage…</font><font color="white"></font>

731
01:05:43.689 --> 01:05:45.900
<font color="white">This is proof that Hye-ri</font><font color="white">
<font color="white">is blessed with good fortune.</font><font color="white"></font></font>

732
01:05:48.361 --> 01:05:50.488
<font color="white">She just delivered herself right to us.</font><font color="white"></font>

733
01:06:54.844 --> 01:06:58.472
<font color="white">AGENT KIM REACTIVATED</font><font color="white"></font>

734
01:06:59.056 --> 01:07:01.308
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Where did you take my daughter?</i></font><font color="white"></font>

735
01:07:01.767 --> 01:07:04.270
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>I love and cherish Hye-ri so much.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

736
01:07:04.353 --> 01:07:06.063
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>no matter what mistakes she makes.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

737
01:07:06.647 --> 01:07:07.857
{\an8}<font color="white">Let's just go through them.</font><font color="white"></font>

738
01:07:09.025 --> 01:07:11.235
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Effective immediately. we're initiating</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>an emergency alert protocol.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

739
01:07:11.318 --> 01:07:13.362
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Is he trying to start a war or what?</i></font><font color="white"></font>

740
01:07:13.446 --> 01:07:15.239
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>They're both after Min-ji right now.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

741
01:07:15.948 --> 01:07:17.408
{\an8}<font color="white">Fire!</font><font color="white"></font>

742
01:07:17.491 --> 01:07:18.659
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>You want to have a shootout?</i></font><font color="white"></font>

743
01:07:18.743 --> 01:07:22.079
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>I can make it</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>so you never see your daughter again.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

744
01:07:22.163 --> 01:07:23.539
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>You can shoot him</i></font><font color="white">
<font color="white"><i>and claim it was an accident.</i></font></font><font color="white"></font>

745
01:07:23.622 --> 01:07:25.458
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Min-ji. I'm here.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

746
01:07:26.500 --> 01:07:27.585
{\an8}<font color="white"><i>Let's go home now.</i></font><font color="white"></font>

747
01:07:28.502 --> 01:07:31.505
{\an8}<font color="white">Subtitle translation by: Jenny Kim</font><font color="white"></font>

748
